race.description: Whitemark Post Office / Cuthill Family Hcp (C1)
race.comment: SNOWDONIA (2) brings strong form to resumption and has trialled well at Longford. Has the inside gate and the leading hoop is reunited. Has a key gear switch and a bold return is likely. STAR FORTIAN (7) resumed on the synthetic and went close from the front when backed off the map. The best of her turf form stacks right up and she's capable of going one better. PRINCE OF KHATUN (5) led and just missed here second-up and has more to give. Was tried at Stakes level before the spell and will keep improving. BLAMEITONTHEBOOGIE (1) was spelled off a solid effort on the synthetic on debut. Has prepared for this with two trial wins and draws an inside barrier. Has to be kept safe.
